    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3463" key="#Princeps">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langubardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, ob
                        salutem anime nostre, <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs><persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Abbots" ref="#people/3469"> Iohannis</persName>
                        venerabili <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> nostri, concedimus in <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs> Beate Sophie</orgName>, ubi <persName
                            ref="#people/3461" key="#Abbesses">Wilerona</persName> religiosissima
                            <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> preesse videtur, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> sacri nostri palatii que dicitur
                        Bubata, que habet <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs> de uno capite fine <placeName
                            ref="#places/3448" key="#Rivers"><rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs>
                            Cerbario</placeName>, de uno latere fine <rs key="#Roads">via
                            puplica</rs> que pergit ad Sanctam Palumbam, de alio capite fine
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3456"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ęcclesia</rs> Sancti Petri</orgName>, de alio quidem
                        latere fine <rs key="#Roads">via alia puplica</rs> que vadit ad casale
                        Buccellati et fine <rs key="#Gualdi">vado</rs> de Mati Lucanis, in integrum
                        cum inferioribus exuperioribus quantum supra dictos fines discernit pertinet
                        de <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Actio"
                            ref="#places/2836"><rs key="#Actio">actu</rs> Sipontino</placeName>, in
                        ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum
                        supra dictas terra sicut supra legitur rectores iam dicti monasterii securo
                        nomine habere et possidere et perfrui valeant et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeant
                        aliquam requisitionem rectores iam phati cenobii, sed perpetuis temporibus
                        possideantur.Quod vero preceptus oblationis ex iussione supra scripte
                        potestatis scripsi ego <persName ref="#people/3465" key="#Notary"
                            >Audoaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> in sacro palatio tertio anno,
                        mense octubrio, quinta indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
